<D>__{a screenplay by james cameron}
<L>__{1 blackness}
<A>__{then two faint lights appear, close together... growing brighter. they resolve into two deep submersibles, free falling toward us like express elevators. one is ahead of the other, and passes close enough to fill frame, looking like a spacecraft blazing with lights, bristling with insectile manipulators. tilting down to follow it as it descends away into the limitless blackness below. soon they are fireflies, then stars. then gone.}
